sentences: Jørgen Træen also known by his stage name Sir Dupermann (born 15 April 1973) is a Norwegian record producer, musician (guitar, keyboards and bass guitar) and electronica artist from Bergen.
In 2002 he released electronica album Sir Dupermann under the artist name 'Sir Dupermann'.
